<item>
            <title>[LU-19464] sanity test_56xb: migrated hard link has mismatched FID</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19464</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e2e92622-d6be-4f03-96f5-c8d50e5e9dac&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e2e92622-d6be-4f03-96f5-c8d50e5e9dac&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_56xb failed with the following error during migration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;igrating files...done
verifying files...done
testing rsync mode when all links fit within xattrs
checking number of hard links listed in xattrs...100
migrating files...
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file30&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file21&apos;: Operation not permitted
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file31&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file21&apos;: Operation not permitted
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file33&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file21&apos;: Operation not permitted
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file34&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file21&apos;: Operation not permitted
ln: failed to create hard link &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file35&apos; =&amp;gt; &apos;/mnt/lustre/d56xb.sanity/file21&apos;: Operation not permitted
migrated hard link has mismatched FID
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117223&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117223&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.76.1.el8_10.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117223&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117223&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.76.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a number of different failures for this subtest. &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19120&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_56xb: Permission denied&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19120&quot;&gt;LU-19120&lt;/a&gt; has different symptoms, but might be related. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first hit is 2025-05-22 on master-next, and all failures have had a master client, even with cases of interop testing with an older server. &lt;/p&gt;

